            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Benhenda, M. 2017. ChemGAN challenge for drug discovery: can AI reproduce natural chemical diversity? <em>arXiv preprint </em><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1708.08227" target="_self">arXiv:1708.08227.</a></p></div></div></div></section><?php include_once 'Elemental/footer.php'; ?>